reviews_data.review_text:
Kanna has quickly become one of my favorite spots in the city. I’ve been coming here for the past few weeks, and every visit has been a 10/10 experience. The environment is the perfect balance between relaxing and productive… whether I need to lock in on work or simply unwind, this place sets the vibe.

What really makes Kanna stand out is the community and the staff. They’re warm, welcoming, and make you feel like family the moment you walk in. I’ve genuinely built great relationships here, which is rare to find in a café/lounge.

As someone who works from home, it’s a huge relief to have a space like this where I can step out of the house, grab quality CBD options, and still stay focused and creative. The atmosphere is stylish yet comfortable, with just the right energy to keep you in the zone.

I’ve been recommending Kanna to everyone I know because it’s more than just a dispensary lounge/café! It’s an experience. Highly recommend checking it out if you’re looking for a place to recharge, connect, and feel inspired.
